  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-status-indicator\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-status-indicator/`\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `list_css_parts`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Dot colors per status, size, pulse animation. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Screen reader text for status. Not color-alone indication. aria-label.\n3. **Functionality** — Status variants (online, offline, busy, away, etc.). Pulse/animation. Size. Text label.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. CSS Parts. Pulse animation. Reduced-motion.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — All API documented.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Variants. ARIA. Animation. Reduced-motion.\n8. **Storybook** — All statuses. With label. Sizes. Animated.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — User status. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
